BUILD
~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*
From the project root, enter the sysmgr directory and run make:
 
	cd sysmgr	
	make
 
Binaries will be placed in the bin/ folder. To do a clean rebuild:
 
	make clean 
 	make
 
 
RUNNING
~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*
Set up the environment
 
	From the project root, run:
 
   	source setup.sh
  
Start the system manager
 
 	From the project root, run:
 
    	sysmgr
IMPORTANT NOTES
~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*
 	All programs must be run from the project root
 
  	source setup.sh must be run before starting any of the programs

	The project is currently built in bin, but rebuilding is recommended